<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>报名申请已提交 | Registration Submitted</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header class="pub-header">
  <div class="container header-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo-area">
      <%- include('./partials/logo') %>
      <div class="site-name">
        硅谷掼蛋联赛
        <small>Silicon Valley Guandan League</small>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</header>

<div style="min-height:calc(100vh - 70px); background:var(--cream); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:40px 20px;">
  <div style="background:white; border-radius:18px; padding:44px 40px; max-width:580px; width:100%; box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);">

    <!-- Pending icon -->
    <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:20px;">
      <div style="font-size:4rem; line-height:1;">⏳</div>
    </div>

    <h1 style="text-align:center; font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:800; color:#641E16; margin-bottom:6px;">
      报名申请已提交！
    </h1>
    <p style="text-align:center; font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:600; color:#922B21; margin-bottom:4px;">
      Registration Submitted!
    </p>
    <p style="text-align:center; font-size:0.9rem; color:#888; margin-bottom:28px;">
      赛事：<strong><%= tournament %></strong>
    </p>

    <!-- Status steps -->
    <div style="border:2px solid #E0D090; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden; margin-bottom:24px;">

      <!-- Step 1 - Done -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; padding:14px 18px; background:#D5F5E3; border-bottom:1px solid #A9DFBF;">
        <div style="width:32px; height:32px; background:#27AE60; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.1rem; flex-shrink:0;">✅</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:700; color:#1A5C34; font-size:0.95rem;">步骤一完成 · Step 1 Done</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:#2ECC71;">报名表已提交 · Registration form submitted</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 - Done (user declared) -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; padding:14px 18px; background:#D5F5E3; border-bottom:1px solid #A9DFBF;">
        <div style="width:32px; height:32px; background:#27AE60; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.1rem; flex-shrink:0;">✅</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:700; color:#1A5C34; font-size:0.95rem;">步骤二完成 · Step 2 Done</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:#2ECC71;">您已声明完成付款 · You declared payment completed</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 - Pending -->
      <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; padding:14px 18px; background:#FEF9E7;">
        <div style="width:32px; height:32px; background:#F39C12; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.1rem; flex-shrink:0; animation:pulse 1.5s infinite;">⏳</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:700; color:#9A7D0A; font-size:0.95rem;">步骤三：等待管理员核实付款 · Step 3: Awaiting Admin Verification</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:#B7950B;">管理员核实您的付款后，报名才正式生效</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.78rem; color:#B7950B;"><em>Registration is confirmed only after admin verifies your payment</em></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Payment reminder -->
    <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FEF9E7,#FDF2D0); border:2px solid #D4AC0D; border-radius:10px; padding:18px 20px; margin-bottom:24px;">
      <div style="font-weight:700; color:#641E16; margin-bottom:10px; font-size:0.97rem;">
        💳 请确认已完成以下任一支付方式 · Please confirm payment via one of:
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px;">
        <div style="background:white; border-radius:8px; padding:12px; text-align:center; border:1.5px solid #E0D090;">
          <div style="font-weight:700; color:#0074DE; margin-bottom:4px;">📱 Venmo</div>
          <div style="font-size:1.2rem; font-weight:900; color:#0074DE;"><%= venmo %></div>
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem; color:#888; margin-top:4px;">金额 Amount: <strong>$<%= fee %></strong></div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:white; border-radius:8px; padding:12px; text-align:center; border:1.5px solid #E0D090;">
          <div style="font-weight:700; color:#07C160; margin-bottom:4px;">💚 微信支付</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.82rem; color:#07C160;">扫描报名页二维码</div>
          <div style="font-size:0.75rem; color:#888; margin-top:4px;">金额 Amount: <strong>$<%= fee %></strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:0.78rem; color:#9A7D0A; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0; text-align:center;">
        ⚠️ 付款备注请注明：<strong>您的姓名 + 赛事名称</strong><br>
        <em>Include in payment note: Your name + Tournament name</em>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Important note -->
    <div style="background:#FADBD8; border-radius:8px; padding:12px 16px; margin-bottom:24px; font-size:0.85rem; color:#922B21; border-left:4px solid #E74C3C;">
      <strong>⚠️ 重要提示 · Important:</strong><br>
      管理员核实付款记录后，您的报名才会被正式确认。如有疑问请联系主办方。<br>
      <em>Your registration will only be officially confirmed after admin verifies payment. Contact the organizer if you have questions.</em>
    </div>

    <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-red">🏠 返回首页 · Home</a>
      <a href="/#tournaments" class="btn btn-gold" style="color:#1C1209">🏆 查看其他赛事 · More</a>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:18px; font-size:0.78rem; color:#bbb;">
      🔒 您的信息已加密保存 | Your information is encrypted<br>
      🐎 2026硅谷掼蛋联赛 · Silicon Valley Guandan League
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: scale(0.95); }
}
</style>

</body>
</html>
